name: Commission of a family
description:
Bristol paper size is 14x17 to accomodate all four subjects.

If you would like to commission a drawing, just send or email 
a photo to me!

The size of paper and the amount of subjects will determine
the price.

name: Isabelle
description:
This an 8x10 commission drawn on watercolor paper.
The paper is not as bright white but gives a more realistic look to 
the subject.

Just email a photo to me or contact me if you would like
me to draw a portrait for you.

name: Competition
description:
This is a sample of a commissioned piece that I have done recently.
This was drawn on 14x17 bristol paper.
Pricing was based on the size, number of subjects and full body view.

If you would like to commission a drawing, just email a photo to me or contact me and we can work out the details!

name: Morey
description:
This is a commissioned piece that I drew
on 11x14 bristol paper.

If you would like to commission a portrait from me
just email a photo to me at lynnieleavitt@yahoo.com
or contact me to mail a copy of a photo to me.
The closer and clearer the better.

One subject, head and shoulders will cost $150.
Full body and background will alter the price.

name: Bella
description:
This is a sample of my work.
It is an 8x10 pencil drawing on bristol paper.

If you would like to commission a portrait from me,
just email a photo to me at lynnieleavitt@yahoo.com 
or send me a copy of a photo you would like me to draw from. 
The closer and clearer, the better.

One subject, head and shoulders, will cost $150.
